Class OACheckBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.jsp.OACheckBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, OATableEditor, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OARadio

    public class OACheckBox
extends java.lang.Object
implements OAJspComponent, OATableEditor
    Controls an html input type=checkbox bind to hub, property show/hide, that can be bound to property enabled, that can be bound to property ajax submit on change
    Author:
    vvia
